{"id":119171,"type":6,"name":"猿飛三世","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/63/1c/119171_4ZATx.jpg","summary":"大坂夏の陣で勝利を収めた徳川家康の軍勢に単身斬り込み、家康を震え上がらせた忍者・猿飛佐助。それから36年経ち、徳川幕府の支配が揺れ動いている江戸時代、山奥で修行に明け暮れる若き忍者がいた。猿飛佐助の孫・佐助、猿飛三世である。佐助はひょんなところから陰謀の渦中にあった小藩の家老の娘・お市を守ろうと、京の町へとやってきた。佐助とその仲間が敵と戦う中で、忍者として人間として成長していきながら、生き別れた父親を追い求めていく。","info":"<li><span>放送星期: </span>金曜日</li><li><span>主演: </span>伊藤淳史 <a href=\"/person/16122\">水川あさみ</a> 柳葉敏郎 浅野ゆう子 堺正章</li><li><span>集数: </span>7</li><li><span>开始: </span>2012-10-12</li><li><span>结束: </span>2012-11-30</li><li><span>类型: </span>時代劇</li><li><span>每集长: </span>43分</li><li><span>频道: </span>NHK BSプレミアム</li><li><span>官方网站: </span>www.nhk.or.jp/jidaigeki/sarutobi</li><li><span>编剧: </span>金子成人 オカモト國ヒコ</li><li><span>导演: </span>石塚嘉 安達もじり</li><li><span>制片: </span>城谷厚司</li>","eps":[{"id":452655,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/452655","type":0,"sort":1,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":452656,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/452656","type":0,"sort":2,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":452657,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/452657","type":0,"sort":3,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":452658,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/452658","type":0,"sort":4,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":452659,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/452659","type":0,"sort":5,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":452660,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/452660","type":0,"sort":6,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":452661,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/452661","type":0,"sort":7,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"}],"staff":[{"id":16122,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/5c/40/16122_prsn_SENBm.jpg","name":"水川麻美","desc":"主演"}]}